 />\n爆一次鹹水 成間屋d 野要換一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dc5a9cc27746b707f36a27f9969d3b44a5fecfc","tid":82002,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T03:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>將軍澳20年垃圾居屋都一萬一呎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳新樓衝到上二萬元呎？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.centanet.com/zh-HK/Home/MDetail/?ID=5256993b-5c87-42ba-a6fe-39f10acb7414\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.centanet.com%2Fzh-HK%2FHome%2FMDetail%2F%3FID%3D5256993b-5c87-42ba-a6fe-39f10acb7414&d=LAMxYje7rJLtKWYjQiVkEnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=e4f568c8\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.centanet.com/zh-HK/Home/MDetail/?ID=5256993b-5c87-42ba-a6fe-39f10acb7414</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現在講緊啟德地價都要萬五元呎，May I recap it in English :係地價<br />\n<br />\n將軍澳咪又係幾千元貨仔地價<br />\n而且將軍澳海量供應，仲要新界扮九龍"},{"pid":"15a5fa0a3e80c14d2e1cb6d794af85e48bab2adb","tid":82002,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T07:09:09.000Z","msg":"平既時候唔識執，貴既時候又買唔起。個時信左報紙佬既，今日後悔都已經太遲。<br />\n<br />\n跟本市區地鐵上蓋新樓就已經無敵，係d on9仔報紙佬嚇下就縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d206a49d136f33bdb16859a01521b1b5e0126cba","tid":82002,"uid":72020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:08:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平既時候唔識執，貴既時候又買唔起。個時信左報紙佬既，今日後悔都已經太遲。<br />\n<br />\n跟本市區地鐵上蓋新樓就已經無敵，係d on9仔報紙佬嚇下就縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔怪得邊個既<br />\n話平都係今日回望過去<br />\n事實上香港啲樓對返當時黎講都係貴<br />\n仲記得讀小學聽到屋企附近地鐵上蓋新樓 <br />\n02年 細單位2m 貴，不了<br />\n09年 4m 貴，不了<br />\n12年 6m 貴，不了<br />\n16年 8m 貴，不了"},{"pid":"7ba92bf8926cb47fe65e3f6cc827e0b3fc2ce486","tid":82002,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T08:49:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平既時候唔識執，貴既時候又買唔起。個時信左報紙佬既，今日後悔都已經太遲。<br />\n<br />\n跟本市區地鐵上蓋新樓就已經無敵，係d on9仔報紙佬嚇下就縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔怪得邊個既<br />\n話平都係今日回望過去<br />\n事實上香港啲樓對返當時黎講都係貴<br />\n仲記得讀小學聽到屋企附近地鐵上蓋新樓 <br />\n02年 細單位2m 貴，不了<br />\n09年 4m 貴，不了<br />\n12年 6m 貴，不了<br />\n16年 8m 貴，不了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中間要加返03，08，同埋15年<br />\n<br />\n跟本係人既問題⋯⋯呢十幾年，租樓用左既錢，一年十幾廿萬，十幾年就百幾二萬。業主就用收返黎既錢又夠比首期買多間。"},{"pid":"79f1b7677de861f801d09abc2ecb3d707e180272","tid":82002,"uid":46120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-16T11:20:45.000Z","msg":"2012年：689上場，樓價一定跌，咪買樓住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300a942e6e98c000d7ddd31323c45e554469f715","tid":82002,"uid":12497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T02:06:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2012年：689上場，樓價一定跌，咪買樓住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7a1a5faaf0a93228bd53067a534499d2060429","tid":82002,"uid":4161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"高登仔人工一早過左<br />\n買條撚咩"},{"pid":"72b98746101779383b3aef5c089b0e84560f5090","tid":82002,"uid":63212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T14:41:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2012年：689上場，樓價一定跌，咪買樓住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n2017: Tsang.."},{"pid":"6358f5bb96966427bf7f586e2b6cec2e9832f3e1","tid":82002,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T23:43:58.000Z","msg":"繼續耻笑<br />\n<br />\n煥然壹居16貨尾單位市價重售　料值逾千萬<br />\n04月18日(二) 19:23   <br />\n<br />\n「煥然壹居」16個賣剩單位將以市價出售，明日出價單。(資料圖片)<br />\n市區重建局首個資助房屋「煥然壹居」16個賣剩單位，將以市價出售，明日(19日)出價單，本月25日抽籤。近期樓市熾熱，啟德新盤呎價已逾2萬港元，而該16個賣剩單位為500多平方呎的兩房單位，當時折扣價約600萬港元，如今市價料逾千萬港元。 <br />\n<br />\n市建局非執行董事麥美娟表示，去年樓市向下，「煥然壹居」因此賣剩單位，當時還擔心重售會跌破折扣價，「如今都唔知道係好定係唔好，樓市升到咁。」她相信該批賣剩單位會受歡迎，但對市場影響不大。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170418/bkn-20170418192328788-0418_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170418%2Fbkn-20170418192328788-0418_00822_001.html&d=LAMxYje7rJLtKWYjQiVkEnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=004d7a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170418/bkn-20170418192328788-0418_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7dbae382f1417872c2fd254620147ad51a464f97","tid":82002,"uid":5584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T04:04:40.000Z","msg":"屌老母現在要8球<br />\n上年六球"},{"pid":"bd65ff40374d97997d16f4edf94eb4abce9f53ac","tid":82002,"uid":51127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T14:48:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌老母現在要8球<br />\n上年六球</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n市建局派錢，個價其實開低左，隔離樓花都萬8起，一買即賺兩球。肯定全城瘋搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c05f07886060f3de5c03c6738d3480d0a7edfbe","tid":82002,"uid":33726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-20T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a4c806d3d41f518c80470b9832f7a4087517d9","tid":82002,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T04:19:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}